name: Rhonda K
text: They still had the bacon,bacon,bacon pizza omg if you haven't tried it try it it's great!

name: Elizabeth Kleier
text: I love the new online ordering system.  Always clean with a friendly staff.  Thin crust is my fave!

name: Alan Stancombe, J.D.
text: The best pizza and price I've ever had

name: Robert Lee
text: Friendly personable staff good with kids a plus that they accept SNAP benefits cards, (a.k.a. EBT) Many different options for toppings and crusts, they have salads, sodas, desserts and bread sticks

name: Felicia Thompson
text: They have a gluten-free option pizza, medium sized pie! And a tomato free sauce!

name: Lexus Stevenson
text: Nice clean, staff is very friendly, good customer service,the pizza is really good I will take this Papa Murphy's over Vallejo Round Table any day!

name: Joseph Garay
text: I'm always happy with my order. The employees are always polite but insincere. Nonetheless I prefer that over apathetic or rude.

name: Glenn Taylor
text: Prefect for those long days and need something fast for dinner ,kids love papa Murphy's

name: John D Baker
text: We love Papa Murphy's! Much better than frozen pizza, and less expensive than soggy delivery pizza.

name: Silverio Sanchez
text: Pizza was good but the young lady that took our order was terrible. Don't think I will be going back any time soon. Truly hope others see this and think about going there just because she had such a terrible attitude.

name: The Rokito
text: Double decker veggie pizzas are great. Need to go back again soon.

name: Bryan Carpenter
text: Better than any frozen pizza you'll put in your oven and cheaper than traditional take out of similar quality.

name: Vincent Copart
text: The staff is always friendly and professional. The food is delicious, and a great value for the money.

name: David Rainey
text: Easy in and out.  Trick is to order and pay online, then there is no waiting at all.

name: Ms Blis
text: Clean place, nice employees and good pizzas

name: Pashion FERRARA - ALDRIDGE
text: Fresh and Fast combined with Cheap and Good= WINNING!

name: ACE-Nation In Love my kids
text: I like the chicken garlic sause pizza Delicious!! plus you cook it @ home.

name: Jehangir Shah
text: I don't remember if it exists now a days or not.....

name: Judy Johnson
